# Manual exclude list – template
# ------------------------------
# When present, this file is passed to rclone bisync via --exclude-from.
# It is meant for PERMANENT, deliberate excludes (as opposed to the
# automatically maintained *.forbidden-deletes.lst, which the script fills itself).
#
# Install per job:
#   cp manual-excludes.example.lst \
#      /mnt/user/appdata/rclone-bisync/state/<REMOTE_NAME>.manual-excludes.lst
#
# Syntax: rclone filter patterns, one pattern per line. Examples:

# Exclude entire folders:
# /old_archive/**
# **/Cache/**

# Single file types:
# *.tmp
# **/*.bak
